{"title":"CSS 實用按鈕 hover 效果","uid":"ac66da125c9b272edffc8fed44e79467","slug":"css-useful-button-hover-effect","date":"2022-12-27T08:02:00.000Z","updated":"2023-01-29T05:14:04.999Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/css-useful-button-hover-effect.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.imgur.com/kL9Sjov.jpg","content":"<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kL9Sjov.jpg\" alt=\"cover\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>先簡單定義一個按鈕 <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> 。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;btnset&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;button&gt;My button&lt;&#x2F;button&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p>如果你要用 <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>，你要把 <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> 放在它裏面，即是：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;button&gt;My button&lt;&#x2F;button&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;</code></pre>\n</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"CSS-變量\"><a href=\"#CSS-變量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CSS 變量\"></a>CSS 變量</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">:root &#123;\n    --primary: #487ff8;\n    --black: #292d3e;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"按鈕設定\"><a href=\"#按鈕設定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"按鈕設定\"></a>按鈕設定</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">button,\nbutton::after &#123;\n    -webkit-transition: all 0.3s;\n    -moz-transition: all 0.3s;\n    -o-transition: all 0.3s;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n    color: #ffffff;\n&#125;\n\nbutton &#123;\n    background: none;\n    border: 3px solid #f1f3f9;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    color: var(--black);\n    font-size: 1em;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    margin: 1em 5px;\n    padding: 1em 3em;\n    position: relative;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n&#125;\n\nbutton::before,\nbutton::after &#123;\n    background: #f1f3f9;\n    content: &#39;&#39;;\n    position: absolute;\n    z-index: -1;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p><code>-webkit-transition</code>、<code>-moz-transition</code> 及 <code>-o-transition</code> 是用來適配其他瀏覽器。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"基本效果\"><a href=\"#基本效果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本效果\"></a>基本效果</h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"由左至右及由右至左設定\"><a href=\"#由左至右及由右至左設定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"由左至右及由右至左設定\"></a><strong>由左至右</strong>及<strong>由右至左</strong>設定</h2><p>基本上由左至右和由右至左都是用這個 CSS：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">.btn::after &#123;\n    height: 100%;\n    top: 0;\n    width: 0;\n&#125;\n\n.btn:hover:after &#123;\n    width: 100%;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"由左至右-Left-to-Right\"><a href=\"#由左至右-Left-to-Right\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"由左至右 (Left to Right)\"></a>由左至右 (Left to Right)</h3><p>加插 <code>left: 0</code> 就能實現。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">.btn::after &#123;\n    ...\n    left: 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"由右至左-Right-to-Left\"><a href=\"#由右至左-Right-to-Left\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"由右至左 (Right to Left)\"></a>由右至左 (Right to Left)</h3><p>加插 <code>right: 0</code> 就能實現。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">.btn::after &#123;\n    ...\n    right: 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"由上至下及由下至上設定\"><a href=\"#由上至下及由下至上設定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"由上至下及由下至上設定\"></a><strong>由上至下</strong>及<strong>由下至上</strong>設定</h2><p>基本上由上至下和由下至上都是用這個 CSS：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">.btn::after &#123;\n    width: 100%;\n    left: 0;\n    height: 0;\n&#125;\n\n.btn:hover:after &#123;\n    height: 100%;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"由上至下-Top-to-Bottom\"><a href=\"#由上至下-Top-to-Bottom\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"由上至下 (Top to Bottom)\"></a>由上至下 (Top to Bottom)</h3><p>加插 <code>top: 0</code> 就能實現。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">.btn::after &#123;\n    ...\n    top: 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"由下至上-Bottom-to-Top\"><a href=\"#由下至上-Bottom-to-Top\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"由下至上 (Bottom to Top)\"></a>由下至上 (Bottom to Top)</h3><p>加插 <code>bottom: 0</code> 就能實現。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">.btn::after &#123;\n    ...\n    bottom: 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"變大及變小設定\"><a href=\"#變大及變小設定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"變大及變小設定\"></a><strong>變大</strong>及<strong>變小</strong>設定</h2><p>主要是用 <code>scale</code> 或 <code>transform: scale()</code> 屬性把其實現。</p>\n<h3 id=\"變大-Zoom-In\"><a href=\"#變大-Zoom-In\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"變大 (Zoom In)\"></a>變大 (Zoom In)</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">.btn:hover &#123;\n    scale: 1.05; &#x2F;* 或者 *&#x2F;\n    transform: scale(1.05)\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"變小-Zoom-Out\"><a href=\"#變小-Zoom-Out\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"變小 (Zoom Out)\"></a>變小 (Zoom Out)</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">.btn:hover &#123;\n    scale: 0.95; &#x2F;* 或者 *&#x2F;\n    transform: scale(0.95)\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"CSS-transform\"><a href=\"#CSS-transform\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CSS transform\"></a>CSS transform</h2><hr>\n<h3 id=\"旋轉-Rotate\"><a href=\"#旋轉-Rotate\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"旋轉 (Rotate)\"></a>旋轉 (Rotate)</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">.btn:hover &#123;\n    transform: rotate(180deg);\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"歪斜-Skew\"><a href=\"#歪斜-Skew\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"歪斜 (Skew)\"></a>歪斜 (Skew)</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">.btn:hover &#123;\n    transform: skew(10deg, 10deg);\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"CSS-animation\"><a href=\"#CSS-animation\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CSS animation\"></a>CSS animation</h2><hr>\n<h3 id=\"發鳴-Hello\"><a href=\"#發鳴-Hello\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"發鳴 (Hello)\"></a>發鳴 (Hello)</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">.btn-hello:hover &#123;\n    animation: hello 2s infinite ease;\n&#125;\n\n@keyframes hello &#123;\n    30% &#123; transform: scale(1.05); &#125;\n    40%, 60% &#123; transform: rotate(-20deg) scale(1.05); &#125;\n    50% &#123; transform: rotate(20deg) scale(1.05); &#125;\n    70% &#123; transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1.05); &#125;\n    100% &#123; transform: scale(1); &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"Codepen-展示\"><a href=\"#Codepen-展示\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Codepen 展示\"></a>Codepen 展示</h1><div class=\"code-toolbar codepen\">\n<iframe src=\"https://codepen.io/bluewhaleyt/embed/preview/abjdvPY?default-tab=result%22\" width=\"100%\" height=\"300\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<hr>\n<p>這篇文章分享一下 CSS 按鈕 hover 效果筆記，文章內容和 Codepen 編碼可能會不定期改進或更新。</p>\n","text":" 先簡單定義一個按鈕 。 基本上由左至右和由右至左都是用這個 CSS： 加插 就能實現。 加插 就能實現。 基本上由上至下和由下至上都是用這個 CSS： 加插 就能實現。 加插 就能實現。 主要是用 或 屬性把其實現。 這篇文章分享一下 CSS 按鈕 hover 效果筆記，文章內...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.6k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"網頁開發","slug":"網頁開發","count":9,"path":"api/categories/網頁開發.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":6,"path":"api/tags/CSS.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#CSS-%E8%AE%8A%E9%87%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">CSS 變量</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8C%89%E9%88%95%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">按鈕設定</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基本效果</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%94%B1%E5%B7%A6%E8%87%B3%E5%8F%B3%E5%8F%8A%E7%94%B1%E5%8F%B3%E8%87%B3%E5%B7%A6%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">由左至右及由右至左設定</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%94%B1%E5%B7%A6%E8%87%B3%E5%8F%B3-Left-to-Right\"><span class=\"toc-text\">由左至右 (Left to Right)</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%94%B1%E5%8F%B3%E8%87%B3%E5%B7%A6-Right-to-Left\"><span class=\"toc-text\">由右至左 (Right to Left)</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%8A%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%8A%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%8B%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">由上至下及由下至上設定</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%8A%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8B-Top-to-Bottom\"><span class=\"toc-text\">由上至下 (Top to Bottom)</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%8B%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8A-Bottom-to-Top\"><span class=\"toc-text\">由下至上 (Bottom to Top)</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%8A%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%8A%E8%AE%8A%E5%B0%8F%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">變大及變小設定</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%8A%E5%A4%A7-Zoom-In\"><span class=\"toc-text\">變大 (Zoom In)</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%8A%E5%B0%8F-Zoom-Out\"><span class=\"toc-text\">變小 (Zoom Out)</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#CSS-transform\"><span class=\"toc-text\">CSS transform</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%97%8B%E8%BD%89-Rotate\"><span class=\"toc-text\">旋轉 (Rotate)</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%AD%AA%E6%96%9C-Skew\"><span class=\"toc-text\">歪斜 (Skew)</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#CSS-animation\"><span class=\"toc-text\">CSS animation</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%99%BC%E9%B3%B4-Hello\"><span class=\"toc-text\">發鳴 (Hello)</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Codepen-%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Codepen 展示</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.ibb.co/zRvn96K/20210718-233824.jpg","link":"/","description":"Everything is possible, as long as you are powerful.","socials":{"github":"http://bit.ly/3WWvvfn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"youtube":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-youtube","link":"https://bit.ly/3C9RlUL"},"facebook":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-facebook","link":null},"instagram":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-instagram","link":null}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"VSCode 自訂程式碼片段","uid":"d834869e51142c9e30211b20e5ae2d70","slug":"vscode-snippet-tutorial","date":"2022-12-31T14:03:21.000Z","updated":"2023-01-28T06:28:59.540Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/vscode-snippet-tutorial.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.imgur.com/7n347Xy.jpg","text":" 哈囉，歡迎來到我的網誌。 有沒有想過自己在編寫程式碼時，能夠借助自動完成選單來完成一整塊的程式碼？在 VSCode 軟件，它能夠支援自訂程式碼片段，使你能夠在輸入關鍵字的前綴後，便能插入一整塊程式碼！大大提升你編程的效率。 在這篇文章，我們將會學到如何新增自己的程式碼片段。 首...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.8k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.ibb.co/zRvn96K/20210718-233824.jpg","link":"/","description":"Everything is possible, as long as you are powerful.","socials":{"github":"http://bit.ly/3WWvvfn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"youtube":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-youtube","link":"https://bit.ly/3C9RlUL"},"facebook":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-facebook","link":null},"instagram":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-instagram","link":null}}}}},"next_post":{"title":"圖片與背景顏色淡入效果","uid":"03e62579958b240dcff8ea639833e129","slug":"photoshop-fade-image-to-color-background","date":"2022-12-26T15:07:17.000Z","updated":"2023-01-29T05:13:51.241Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/photoshop-fade-image-to-color-background.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.imgur.com/ExPH5sv.jpg","text":" 這篇文章是簡單記錄一下用 Photoshop 製作圖片與背景顏色淡入效果。 首先，新建文件，我會以 （寬度：1280像素；高度：720像素） 作為這個圖片的解像度。 在上方找 > ，再選擇想插入的圖片。 例如我選擇了這個圖片。 長按 鍵再長按鼠標左鍵，把圖像移到你想要的位置，完...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":634,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Photoshop","slug":"Photoshop","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Photoshop.json"}],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.ibb.co/zRvn96K/20210718-233824.jpg","link":"/","description":"Everything is possible, as long as you are powerful.","socials":{"github":"http://bit.ly/3WWvvfn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"youtube":{"ic